title: [Treasure Trove, Back Room]
description: Darkness reigns in this tiny cavern.  The only light is an ambient, faint greenish glow that seems to emanate from the rocks themselves, and flickering firelight emitted from a jagged crack in one wall.  Shadowy shapes loom in the periphery of vision that could be anything from a stalactite to a vicious cave dweller.

Darkness reigns in this tiny cavern.  The only light is an ambient, faint greenish glow that seems to emanate from the rocks themselves, and flickering firelight emitted from a jagged crack in one wall.  Just inside the edge of light is a dark stone shelf holding a stack of rectangular objects.  Shadowy shapes loom in the periphery of vision that could be anything from a stalactite to a vicious cave dweller.
